                <h1>Research group tracks elephants to help better protect them from poaching</h1>
                
                                    <figure class="dom-art-container my-4">
                                                    <img src="https://snworksceo.imgix.net/dtc/02192218-80d3-4c35-9e49-6ce90e60e116.sized-1000x1000.jpg?w=1000" alt="&lt;p&gt;The&#x20;researchers&#x20;are&#x20;working&#x20;to&#x20;identify&#x20;areas&#x20;that&#x20;the&#x20;Gabon&#x20;Park&#x20;Agency&#x20;can&#x20;better&#x20;protect&#x20;to&#x20;help&amp;nbsp&#x3B;prevent&#x20;the&#x20;elephant&#x20;populations&#x27;&#x20;decline.&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;" class="w-100">
                                                <div class="domphoto-caption mt-2 text-left text-md-right">
                            <p>The researchers are working to identify areas that the Gabon Park Agency can better protect to help&nbsp;prevent the elephant populations' decline.</p>

                            
                        </div>
                    </figure>
                
                                    <div class="row  mt-4 mb-0 mb-md-4">
                        <div class="col-12 col-md-6">
                            <aside class="author-name">
                                    
    
                                    
            By <a href="https://www.dukechronicle.com/staff/bre-bradham">Bre Bradham</a>
                                    
                                <div class="mt-1">
                                    <span class="can-localize">January 12, 2017 | 12:27am EST</span>
                                </div>
                            </aside>
                        </div>
                        <div class="col-12 col-md-6 text-left text-md-right d-print-none">
                            <ul class="social-links list-unsyled list-inline mt-4 mt-md-0">
                                <li class="list-inline-item"><a href="http://www.facebook.com/sharer.php?u=https://www.dukechronicle.com/article/2017/01/research-group-tracks-elephants-to-help-better-protect-them-from-poaching" target="_blank" class="sends-events" data-ga-category="Share" data-ga-action="click" data-ga-label="facebook" data-ga-value="CURL"><i class="fab fa-facebook"></i></a></li>
